Entry.EnglishText: I wonder how my sister is doing...

Entry.JapaneseText: またセレーナさんのコト？ いい加減、お姉さんばなれしたら？
Entry.EnglishText: Are you thinking about Selena again? How about you stop being so clingy towards her?

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ、そうだよな。姉貴だって、いつかは お嫁に行っちまうんだしな！
Entry.EnglishText: Yeah, you're right. She's going to get married eventually, after all!

Entry.JapaneseText: そうだよ、<Tytree>！ ここはひとつ、恋でもしてみたら？
Entry.EnglishText: That's right, <Tytree>! Wanna try falling in love too?
Sure, I'll give it a shot!

Entry.JapaneseText: 姉貴みたいな子はどっかにいねーかなぁ……？
Entry.EnglishText: Now, where to find a girl like my sister...?
